
---


@startuml
' Entities involved in the cinema booking system

class Cinema {
    - id: int
    - name: string
    - town: string
}

class Theatre {
    - id: int
    - name: string
    - capacity: int
    - cinema: Cinema
}

class Movie {
    - title: string
    - duration: int (minutes)
    - releaseDate: Date
}

class Copy {
    - id: int
    - movie: Movie
    - cinema: Cinema
}

class Show {
    - id: int
    - startTime: DateTime
    - endTime: DateTime
    - theatre: Theatre
    - copy: Copy
}

class Reservation {
    - id: int
    - customerEmail: string
    - seatNumber: int
    - show: Show
    - reservationTime: DateTime
    - cancellationTime: DateTime (nullable)
    - status: Status (Pending / Cancelled / Confirmed)
}

class Ticket {
    - id: int
    - seatNumber: int
    - show: Show
    - purchaseTime: DateTime
    - type: string (OnlineReservation / OnSite)
}

class FreeTicketOffer {
    - id: int
    - newShow: Show
    - newSeatNumber: int
    - expirationTime: DateTime
    - accepted: boolean
    - reservation: Reservation
}

class Customer {
    - email: string
    - firstName: string
    - lastName: string
}

class CreditCard {
    - number: string
    - cvv: string
    - expiry: string
    - customer: Customer
}

class Payment {
    - id: int
    - amount: decimal
    - paymentTime: DateTime
    - creditCard: CreditCard
    - reservation: Reservation
}

class Display {
    - availableSeats: int
    - show: Show
}

class Programming {
    - startDate: Date
    - endDate: Date
    - publishedOn: DateTime
    - shows: list<Show>
}

' Associations

Cinema "1" *-- "many" Theatre : contains
Theatre "1" o-- "many" Show : hosts
Copy "1" -- "many" Show : used in
Cinema "1" *-- "many" Copy : owns
Movie "1" *-- "many" Copy : has copies of

Show "1" -- "many" Reservation : has
Show "1" -- "many" Ticket : has
Reservation "1" -- "1" Payment : paid with
Reservation "1" -- "0..1" FreeTicketOffer : may have
Customer "1" -- "many" CreditCard : owns
CreditCard "1" -- "many" Payment : used for
Customer "1" -- "many" Reservation : made by
Show "1" -- "1" Display : displayed on
Programming "1" -- "many" Show : includes

enum Status {
    Pending
    Cancelled
    Confirmed
}

@enduml

---

### 🧩 Explanation of Key Elements:

- **Cinema**: A location that can contain multiple theatres.
- **Theatre**: A room inside a cinema where shows are played.
- **Movie & Copy**: Each movie has one or more physical copies stored at specific cinemas.
- **Show**: A scheduled screening of a movie copy in a theatre.
- **Reservation & Ticket**: Customers can reserve seats online or buy tickets on-site. Reservations are refundable under certain conditions.
- **FreeTicketOffer**: An offer to rebook when a show is canceled.
- **Payment**: Only debited after the cancellation period ends.
- **Display**: Shows how many seats are left for a particular show.
- **Programming**: Weekly schedule from Wednesday to Tuesday.

